# React Doctor

After making React code changes, run:

    npx react-doctor@latest --verbose --scope changed

Check the health score did not regress. If it dropped, fix the regressions before committing.

For a full cleanup pass, run `npx react-doctor@latest --verbose` and fix by severity (errors first, then warnings).

Full skill (triage playbook, rule config): see `.cursor/skills/react-doctor/SKILL.md`.
